ts/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76edfc43e1d6f4056231783d4d8cc267e3eaab43","tid":162058,"uid":90415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"有左人造人<br />\n有咩病都可以換曬自己既心肝脾肺腎"},{"pid":"b8eaf028a17875f5adf57e6d20114b4a673d1124","tid":162058,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有左人造人<br />\n有咩病都可以換曬自己既心肝脾肺腎</blockquote><br />\n道德問題，等同殺人<br />\n參考資料：the island (2005)"},{"pid":"4cb4aa49ef11c1e94016d577eb009b0e872a75c8","tid":162058,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"其實我最想佢重現返呢D︰<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴龍 (T-REX)<br />\n三角龍(Triceratops)<br />\n長毛象<br />\n劍齒虎<br />\n魚龍<br />\n翼龍<br />\n三葉蟲<br />\n菊石</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"2fcaa026cb9131c2f8c96ac7c00a20e15af5b5ae","tid":162058,"uid":33915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有左人造人<br />\n有咩病都可以換曬自己既心肝脾肺腎</blockquote><br />\n道德問題，等同殺人<br />\n參考資料：the island (2005)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點知邊個先係真正既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d232450030487a948463aa28467ed419c6110a11","tid":162058,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理論物理學教授加來道雄（Michio Kaku）</span></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪專吹水？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/120454_25f42677b78cdc11059b6720ab035040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F120454_25f42677b78cdc11059b6720ab035040.jpg&h=e68fceab&s={SIZE}\" />呢條友好似成日上discovery channel 既科學節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n物理佢真係勁，但係其它科學範疇都係吹㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8f7b8fa562e6e348321444a488f59ebaae903d","tid":162058,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"高達天人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dd5d00f32f886168442bde5fd7e0ea867fc090","tid":162058,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理論物理學教授加來道雄（Michio Kaku）</span></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪專吹水？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/120454_25f42677b78cdc11059b6720ab035040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F120454_25f42677b78cdc11059b6720ab035040.jpg&h=e68fceab&s={SIZE}\" />呢條友好似成日上discovery channel 既科學節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n物理佢真係勁，但係其它科學範疇都係吹㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔撚係佢複製，你放大黎做乜<br />\n佢係提出左倫理嘅問題，你閱讀理解係咪u9左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b88d3c808181891c3c4e55a29d509edf5c8147b","tid":162058,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"複製人智商係點計呢？<br />\n 如果複製愛恩斯坦會點 ？<br />\n雖然話後天有影響，咁先天呢？"},{"pid":"8922bbc84b0e02961892a3fb5066c9b4731167eb","tid":162058,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"現階段複製技術都要靠母體進行 好似喺<br />\n當有一日機械取代母體嘅功能複製生命<br />\n世界究竟會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0b2eef924ebb5c158b11e43bba962895e215d9","tid":162058,"uid":90749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上帝創造恐龍<br />\n上帝毀滅恐龍<br />\n上帝創造人類<br />\n人類創造科學<br />\n科學毀滅上帝<br />\n人類創造恐龍<br />\n科學毀滅人類</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndinosaur eats men,<br />\nwomen inherits the earth"},{"pid":"54324da809c1e1e6832c37291b84705c20cc37ce","tid":162058,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>複製人智商係點計呢？<br />\n 如果複製愛恩斯坦會點 ？<br />\n雖然話後天有影響，咁先天呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我假設佢所講既複製技術，係指將複複製者過身一刻（因為DNA synthesis 到個一刻為止）複製，延續落去，而唔係用杯胎從小培養，所以不存在先天被後天因素影響。"},{"pid":"d5bb233116deb41290bd639165dd6e661c0272d2","tid":162058,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現階段複製技術都要靠母體進行 好似喺<br />\n當有一日機械取代母體嘅功能複製生命<br />\n世界究竟會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主流社會以二元男女婚姻佢為基礎，某程度係因為男女生育問題。就你所講，我首先諗到會係婚姻制度崩壞。"},{"pid":"d83bf7fd727774d286eb3b6bb351b6561861c97d","tid":162058,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上帝創造恐龍<br />\n上帝毀滅恐龍<br />\n上帝創造人類<br />\n人類創造科學<br />\n科學毀滅上帝<br />\n人類創造恐龍<br />\n科學毀滅人類</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndinosaur eats men,<br />\nwomen inherits the earth</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/dORJLkf0wGVI4/200_s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FdORJLkf0wGVI4%2F200_s.gif&h=61e341f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecc128bd657c2321c23e98825b8980517a571b1","tid":162058,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>複製人智商係點計呢？<br />\n 如果複製愛恩斯坦會點 ？<br />\n雖然話後天有影響，咁先天呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我假設佢所講既複製技術，係指將<span style=\"color: red;\">複</span>複製者過身一刻（因為DNA synthesis 到個一刻為止）複製，延續落去，而唔係用杯胎從小培養，所以不存在先天被後天因素影響。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n被複制者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dcf618d0fa7a19579dc7423c1727cf2db071fb","tid":162058,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3cd4aefe35bae4947576aa674323baea63053c","tid":162058,"uid":71697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"依種技術一早做到啦！啲人做完唔話你知咋嘛！"},{"pid":"a59d6fbe2b865dfc01cb5fdf1f17f76e466b4e60","tid":162058,"uid":56299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"其實複製左都只係為左滿足科學家嘅研究慾望 對於人類嘅未來係有益咩？"},{"pid":"558a871db7082577c0f7bba8cd46e3036126bb46","tid":162058,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理論