chio Kaku）</span></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪專吹水？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/120454_25f42677b78cdc11059b6720ab035040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F120454_25f42677b78cdc11059b6720ab035040.jpg&h=e68fceab&s={SIZE}\" />呢條友好似成日上discovery channel 既科學節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n物理佢真係勁，但係其它科學範疇都係吹㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔撚係佢複製，你放大黎做乜<br />\n佢係提出左倫理嘅問題，你閱讀理解係咪u9左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪即係吹水囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相對論未證實之前都被視為吹水<br />\n理論物理太高level<br />\n一般人會覺得係吹水野</blockquote><br />\n倫理問題呀吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱智仔吹水同意見都唔識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5915706022e05c0526b1e121b2b155f51f9a8f36","tid":162058,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"理乜9倫理問題呀，到時自然會孕育出有新倫理系統去說服全人類，現時嘅倫理系統都漸漸過時"},{"pid":"e6399ff342ca143439d0e83225b40674cf75aa49","tid":162058,"uid":31745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"唉屌呢班濕鳩科學家唔好搞咁撚多嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716a354002cd1a82c4a9fa3f61835d5596071ab6","tid":162058,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:13:10.000Z","msg":"複製技術無乜普及化嘅用途<br />\n可以咁講 複製技術只喺人類嘅一個成就<br />\n但喺對提升人類生活或心理素質無幫助"},{"pid":"5dc0a3360533860d6641e3f64b756e5f844f58cb","tid":162058,"uid":16384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>複製技術無乜普及化嘅用途<br />\n可以咁講 複製技術只喺人類嘅一個成就<br />\n但喺對提升人類生活或心理素質無幫助</blockquote><br />\n錯啦<br />\n複製技術成功嘅話係可以發展到再生技術"},{"pid":"09ddedbe03dd58fd51a7c37074e9279b609ab051","tid":162058,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理乜9倫理問題呀，到時自然會孕育出有新倫理系統去說服全人類，現時嘅倫理系統都漸漸過時</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得以現時既倫理道德標準，其實有好多新既科技發展（如種植器官、優生學去除不良基因）根本無可能展現人間。你地唔覺得60-90年代科技發展迅速，好多我地今時今日用到既野如電話，電腦都係個時開始發明同普及。呢十幾年，可能正如上面有位巴打講「整左都唔人知咋嘛」，其實係我地日常生活中背後以經有呢方面既科技。<br />\n<br />\n所以，道得觀既突破，可能比起技術層面更需要我地去注視。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c19297b4dd7aa719ca71ce8717f1459e425077","tid":162058,"uid":17883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上帝創造恐龍<br />\n上帝毀滅恐龍<br />\n上帝創造人類<br />\n人類創造科學<br />\n科學毀滅上帝<br />\n人類創造恐龍<br />\n科學毀滅人類</blockquote><br />\nOn9<br />\n你信上帝？"},{"pid":"7846636c354ef5655360f8725f3301da9ca503e5","tid":162058,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上帝創造恐龍<br />\n上帝毀滅恐龍<br />\n上帝創造人類<br />\n人類創造科學<br />\n科學毀滅上帝<br />\n人類創造恐龍<br />\n科學毀滅人類</blockquote><br />\nOn9<br />\n你信上帝？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喻體<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔啱聽可以用其他野比喻（基因/自然 etc)"},{"pid":"40ac512d2f872d7f71c27951b0cdde456374580e","tid":162058,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上帝創造恐龍<br />\n上帝毀滅恐龍<br />\n上帝創造人類<br />\n人類創造科學<br />\n科學毀滅上帝<br />\n人類創造恐龍<br />\n科學毀滅人類</blockquote><br />\nOn9<br />\n你信上帝？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喻體<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔啱聽可以用其他野比